::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_100050306-->
::{{A|VO chapter0 7 welt 103.ogg}} '''Welt:''' ...I'll check you out in a minute.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Very tasteful.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_100050309-->
::{{A|VO chapter0 7 welt 105.ogg}} '''Welt:''' Tasteful... Oh, you mean the train? I was asking how you felt physically.
