:<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_100050311-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_100050311-->
:{{A|VO chapter0 7 welt 107.ogg}} '''Welt:''' In any case, I have to thank you for saving March.
:<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_1000503_29-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_1000503_29-->
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} You guys saved me, too.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_100050313-->
