::{{A|VO chapter0 7 welt 109.ogg}} '''Welt:''' ...I don't want to frighten you, but the truth is you won't ever be in the clear while it is still inside your body.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} I couldn't just stand by and watch.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_100050316-->
::{{A|VO chapter0 7 welt 110.ogg}} '''Welt:''' It's good that you think so. Someone with that mindset and the actions to back it up &mdash; that is the true meaning of the word "hero."
