::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_100050317-->
::{{A|VO chapter0 7 welt 111.ogg}} '''Welt:''' Helping others without a second thought &mdash; that is the most important quality of a hero.
:<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_100050318-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_100050318-->
:{{A|VO chapter0 7 welt 112.ogg}} '''Welt:''' However, as long as the Stellaron is still in your body, you should be careful what you do. I don't know if Himeko and I can suppress it again.
